<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>ASIAA Travel - Privacy Policy</title>

  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

  <style>

    *{
      margin:0;
      padding:0;
      box-sizing:border-box;
    }

    body{
      font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top left,#fff3c4,transparent 35%),
        radial-gradient(circle at bottom right,#ffe082,transparent 35%),
        linear-gradient(135deg,#fffdf5,#fff8e1,#fffde7);
      min-height:100vh;
      padding:40px 20px;
      color:#2b2b2b;
    }

    /* =========================
       CONTAINER
    ========================== */

    .policy-container{
      max-width:1100px;
      margin:auto;
      border-radius:30px;
      overflow:hidden;
      background:#ffffffee;
      border:1px solid #ffe082;
      box-shadow:
        0 12px 35px rgba(255,193,7,0.18),
        0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    }

    /* =========================
       HEADER
    ========================== */

    .policy-header{
      position:relative;
      padding:90px 50px;
      text-align:center;
      overflow:hidden;
      background:
        linear-gradient(135deg,#ffd54f,#ffc107,#ffca28);
    }

    .policy-header::before{
      content:"";
      position:absolute;
      width:420px;
      height:420px;
      border-radius:50%;
      background:#ffffff30;
      top:-220px;
      right:-120px;
    }

    .policy-header::after{
      content:"";
      position:absolute;
      width:280px;
      height:280px;
      border-radius:50%;
      background:#fff9c433;
      bottom:-150px;
      left:-80px;
    }

    /* =========================
   CLEAN HEADER STYLE
========================== */

.policy-header{
  padding: 80px 40px;
  text-align: center;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg,#ffd54f,#ffc107,#ffca28);
}

.policy-header h1{
  font-size: 58px;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: #4e342e;
  margin-bottom: 12px;
  letter-spacing: 1px;
}

.policy-header p{
  color: #5d4037;
  font-size: 17px;
  font-weight: 500;
}

    /* =========================
       CONTENT
    ========================== */

    .policy-content{
      padding:50px;
    }

    .policy-section{
      margin-bottom:30px;
      padding:30px;
      border-radius:24px;
      background:#fffdf7;
      border:1px solid #ffe082;
      transition:0.35s ease;
    }

    .policy-section:hover{
      transform:translateY(-5px);
      box-shadow:0 12px 28px rgba(255,193,7,0.15);
      border-color:#ffc107;
    }

    .policy-section h2{
      font-size:25px;
      margin-bottom:18px;
      font-weight:700;
      color:#ff9800;
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      gap:12px;
    }

    .policy-section h2::before{
      content:"";
      width:12px;
      height:12px;
      border-radius:50%;
      background:#ffc107;
      box-shadow:0 0 14px #ffc107;
    }

    .policy-section p{
      color:#555;
      font-size:15.5px;
      line-height:1.9;
    }

    .policy-section ul{
      margin-top:16px;
      padding-left:18px;
    }

    .policy-section ul li{
      margin-bottom:14px;
      color:#444;
    }

    /* =========================
       HIGHLIGHT BOX
    ========================== */

    .highlight-box{
      margin-top:18px;
      padding:22px;
      border-radius:18px;
      background:linear-gradient(135deg,#fff9c4,#fff3b0);
      border:1px solid #ffd54f;
      color:#5d4037;
      font-weight:500;
    }

    /* =========================
       FOOTER
    ========================== */

    .footer-note{
      text-align:center;
      padding:28px;
      border-top:1px solid #ffe082;
      color:#666;
      font-size:14px;
      background:#fff8e1;
    }

    /* =========================
       ANIMATIONS
    ========================== */

    @keyframes floatText{
      0%{
        transform:translateY(0px);
      }

      50%{
        transform:translateY(-6px);
      }

      100%{
        transform:translateY(0px);
      }
    }

    @keyframes bubbleMove{
      0%{
        transform:translateY(0) scale(1);
        opacity:0.5;
      }

      50%{
        transform:translateY(-12px) scale(1.1);
        opacity:0.8;
      }

      100%{
        transform:translateY(0) scale(1);
        opacity:0.5;
      }
    }

    /* =========================
       RESPONSIVE
    ========================== */

    @media(max-width:768px){

      body{
        padding:20px 12px;
      }

      .policy-header{
        padding:70px 25px;
      }

      .policy-header h1{
        font-size:40px;
      }

      .policy-content{
        padding:24px;
      }

      .policy-section{
        padding:22px;
      }

      .policy-section h2{
        font-size:21px;
      }

      .policy-section p,
      .policy-section li{
        font-size:14px;
      }
    }

  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <div class="policy-container">

    <div class="policy-header">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p>ASIAA Travel Driver Application</p>
    </div>

    <div class="policy-content">

      <div class="policy-section">
        <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
        <p>
          Welcome to ASIAA Travel. Your privacy is important to us.
          This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, store,
          and protect your personal information when using our services.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-section">
        <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>

        <ul>
          <li>Full Name</li>
          <li>Phone Number</li>
          <li>Email Address</li>
          <li>Driver License Details</li>
          <li>Vehicle Registration Information</li>
          <li>Insurance Documents</li>
          <li>Government ID Proof</li>
          <li>Location & GPS Data</li>
          <li>Payment Information</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-section">
        <h2>3. How We Use Information</h2>

        <p>
          Your information is used for account verification,
          ride management, payment processing, safety monitoring,
          and improving our transportation services.
        </p>

        <div class="highlight-box">
          We never sell your personal information to third parties.
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-section">
        <h2>4. Data Security</h2>

        <p>
          We use reasonable security measures to protect your data
          against unauthorized access, disclosure, or misuse.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-section">
        <h2>5. Driver Rights</h2>

        <ul>
          <li>Access personal information</li>
          <li>Update inaccurate information</li>
          <li>Request account deletion</li>
          <li>Withdraw permissions where applicable</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-section">
        <h2>6. Contact Us</h2>

        <div class="highlight-box">
          <strong>Email:</strong> support@asiaa-travel.com <br>
        <strong>Phone:</strong> +91 9514228005 <br>
        <strong>Company:</strong> Asiaa Travel
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="footer-note">
      © 2026 ASIAA Travel. All Rights Reserved.
    </div>

  </div>

</body>
</html>